response.original_title: WWE: Undertaker - This Is My Yard
response.overview: Covers The Undertaker's career from his arrival in NWA/WCW as "Mean" Mark Callous as the replacement for Sid Vicious in the Skyscrapers through his first "Decade of Destruction" in WWE, from his surprise debut at "Survivor Series 1990" through his feud with Diamond Dallas Page.
response.title: WWE: Undertaker - This Is My Yard
